<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov-o> <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#description> "Ontologi som beskriver marine observatorier (regionale fasiliteter, steder, plattformer) for å støtte FAIR datastyring og interoperabilitet, spesielt i EMSO ERIC-konteksten."@no .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov-o> <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#description> "Ontologia care descrie observatoarele marine (facilități regionale, situri, platforme) pentru a susține gestionarea FAIR a datelor și interoperabilitatea, în special în contextul EMSO ERIC."@ro .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov-o> <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#description> "Ontologia che descrive gli osservatori marini (infrastrutture regionali, siti, piattaforme) per supportare la gestione FAIR dei dati e l’interoperabilità, in particolare nel contesto EMSO ERIC."@it .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov-o> <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#description> "Ontologia que descreve os observatórios marinhos (infraestruturas regionais, locais, plataformas) para apoiar a gestão FAIR de dados e a interoperabilidade, especialmente no contexto do EMSO ERIC."@pt .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov-o> <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#description> "Ontologie décrivant les observatoires marins (infrastructures régionales, sites, plateformes) pour soutenir la gestion FAIR des données et l’interopérabilité, notamment dans le cadre d’EMSO ERIC."@fr .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov-o> <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#description> "Ontology describing marine observatories (Regional Facilities, Sites, Platforms) to support FAIR data management and interoperability, particularly in the EMSO ERIC context."@en .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov-o> <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#description> "Ontología que describe los observatorios marinos (infraestructuras regionales, sitios, plataformas) para apoyar la gestión FAIR de datos y la interoperabilidad, especialmente en el contexto de EMSO ERIC."@es .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov-o> <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#description> "Οντολογία που περιγράφει τα θαλάσσια παρατηρητήρια (περιφερειακές υποδομές, τοποθεσίες, πλατφόρμες) για την υποστήριξη της διαχείρισης δεδομένων FAIR και της διαλειτουργικότητας, ιδιαίτερα στο πλαίσιο του EMSO ERIC."@el .
