<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov-o> <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology> "Co-construcción con expertos del dominio y alineación iterativa con ontologías de referencia"@es .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov-o> <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology> "Co-construction avec des experts métier et alignement itératif avec des ontologies de référence"@fr .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov-o> <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology> "Co-construction with domain experts and iterative alignment with reference ontologies"@en .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov-o> <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology> "Co-construcție cu experți din domeniu și aliniere iterativă cu ontologii de referință"@ro .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov-o> <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology> "Co-construção com especialistas no domínio e alinhamento iterativo com ontologias de referência"@pt .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov-o> <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology> "Co-costruzione con esperti di dominio e allineamento iterativo con ontologie di riferimento"@it .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov-o> <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology> "Samskaping med fagpersoner og iterativ tilpasning til referanseontologier"@no .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov-o> <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology> "Συνεκπόνηση με ειδικούς του τομέα και επαναληπτική ευθυγράμμιση με πρότυπες οντολογίες"@el .
