<http://www.w3.org/2003/01/geo/wgs84_pos#SpatialThing> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Anything with spatial extent, i.e. size, shape, or position.\n e.g. people, places, bowling balls, as well as abstract areas like cubes.\n" .
<http://www.w3.org/2003/01/geo/wgs84_pos#SpatialThing> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "SpatialThing" .
