# https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#FundedProject
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#FundedProject> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#FundedProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchProject> .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#FundedProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A research project supported by dedicated financial funding from one or more organizations or funding bodies."@en .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#FundedProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Et forskningsprosjekt støttet av dedikert finansiering fra en eller flere organisasjoner eller finansieringskilder."@no .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#FundedProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Um projeto de investigação apoiado por financiamento específico proveniente de uma ou mais organizações ou entidades financiadoras."@pt .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#FundedProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un progetto di ricerca sostenuto da finanziamenti dedicati provenienti da una o più organizzazioni o enti finanziatori."@it .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#FundedProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un proiect de cercetare susținut prin finanțare dedicată din partea uneia sau mai multor organizații sau organisme de finanțare."@ro .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#FundedProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un projet de recherche soutenu par un financement dédié provenant d'une ou plusieurs organisations ou agences de financement."@fr .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#FundedProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un proyecto de investigación respaldado por financiación específica de una o más organizaciones o entidades financiadoras."@es .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#FundedProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Ένα ερευνητικό έργο που υποστηρίζεται από ειδική χρηματοδότηση από έναν ή περισσότερους οργανισμούς ή φορείς χρηματοδότησης."@el .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#FundedProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Finansiert prosjekt"@no .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#FundedProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Funded project"@en .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#FundedProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Progetto finanziato"@it .
