# 
# https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Platform
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Platform> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Platform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Subsite> .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Platform> <http://data.bioontology.org/metadata/prefixIRI> "OSO:Platform" .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Platform> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/source> <http://vocab.nerc.ac.uk/collection/L06/current/> .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Platform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An observation platform, fixed or mobile, installed on a site or subsite, supporting one or more instruments or acquisition systems."@en .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Platform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "En observasjonsplattform, fast eller mobil, installert på et sted eller underområde, som støtter ett eller flere instrumenter eller innhentingssystemer."@no .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Platform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "O platformă de observație, fixă sau mobilă, instalată într-un site sau subsite, care suportă unul sau mai multe instrumente sau sisteme de achiziție."@ro .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Platform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Uma plataforma de observação, fixa ou móvel, instalada num local ou sublocal, suportando um ou mais instrumentos ou sistemas de aquisição."@pt .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Platform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Una piattaforma di osservazione, fissa o mobile, installata su un sito o sotto-sito, che supporta uno o più strumenti o sistemi di acquisizione."@it .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Platform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Una plataforma de observación, fija o móvil, instalada en un sitio o sub-sitio, que soporta uno o más instrumentos o sistemas de adquisición."@es .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Platform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Une plateforme d'observation fixe ou mobile, installée sur un site ou un sous-site, supportant un ou plusieurs instruments ou systèmes d'acquisition."@fr .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Platform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Μια πλατφόρμα παρατήρησης, σταθερή ή κινητή, εγκατεστημένη σε έναν τόπο ή υποτοποθεσία, υποστηρίζοντας ένα ή περισσότερα όργανα ή συστήματα συλλογής δεδομένων."@el .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Platform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Observasjonsplattform"@no .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Platform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Observation Platform"@en .
