# 
# https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Thing> .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility> <http://data.bioontology.org/metadata/prefixIRI> "OSO:RegionalFacility" .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A regional facility containing sites, associated with research infrastructures, oceanographic campaigns, organizations, and a Regional Team Leader."@en .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Infraestructura regional que contiene sitios, asociada a infraestructuras de investigación, campañas oceanográficas, organizaciones y un líder de equipo regional."@es .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Infraestrutura regional que contém locais, associada a infraestruturas de investigação, campanhas oceanográficas, organizações e um líder regional."@pt .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Infrastructură regională care conține site-uri, asociată cu infrastructuri de cercetare, campanii oceanografice, organizații și un lider de echipă regional."@ro .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Infrastruttura regionale contenente siti, associata a infrastrutture di ricerca, campagne oceanografiche, organizzazioni e un coordinatore regionale."@it .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Regional fasilitet som inneholder lokaliteter, tilknyttet forskningsinfrastrukturer, havkampanjer, organisasjoner og en regionalt ansvarlig."@no .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Une noeud régional comprenant plusieurs sites, liée à des infrastructures de recherche, des campagnes océanographiques, des organisations et un coordinateur régional."@fr .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Περιφερειακή υποδομή που περιλαμβάνει τοποθεσίες, συνδέεται με ερευνητικές υποδομές, ωκεανογραφικές εκστρατείες, οργανισμούς και έναν υπεύθυνο ομάδας."@el .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Infraestructura regional"@es .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Infraestrutura regional"@pt .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Infrastructură regională"@ro .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Infrastruttura regionale"@it .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Nœud régional"@fr .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Regional Facility"@en .
