# 
# https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchProject
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchProject> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Project> .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A structured scientific activity designed to produce new knowledge, data, or understanding within a defined scope and duration."@en .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "En strukturert vitenskapelig aktivitet som har som mål å produsere ny kunnskap, data eller forståelse innenfor et definert omfang og tidsrom."@no .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "O activitate științifică structurată destinată să producă noi cunoștințe, date sau înțelegere într-un cadru și o durată definite."@ro .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Uma atividade científica estruturada concebida para produzir novo conhecimento, dados ou compreensão dentro de um âmbito e duração definidos."@pt .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un'attività scientifica strutturata progettata per produrre nuova conoscenza, dati o comprensione entro un ambito e una durata definiti."@it .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Una actividad científica estructurada destinada a producir nuevo conocimiento, datos o comprensión dentro de un alcance y una duración definidos."@es .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Une activité scientifique structurée visant à produire de nouvelles connaissances, données ou compréhensions dans un périmètre et une durée définis."@fr .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Επιστημονική δραστηριότητα με σαφή δομή που αποσκοπεί στην παραγωγή νέας γνώσης, δεδομένων ή κατανόησης, εντός καθορισμένου πλαισίου και διάρκειας."@el .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Forskningsprosjekt"@no .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Progetto di ricerca"@it .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Proiect de cercetare"@ro .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Projet de recherche"@fr .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Projeto de investigação"@pt .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Proyecto de investigación"@es .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Research project"@en .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Ερευνητικό έργο"@el .
# 
# https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#SeriesOfOceanographicCampaigns
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#SeriesOfOceanographicCampaigns> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#SeriesOfOceanographicCampaigns> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Thing> .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#SeriesOfOceanographicCampaigns> <http://data.bioontology.org/metadata/prefixIRI> "omv:SeriesOfOceanographicCampaigns" .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#SeriesOfOceanographicCampaigns> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A series of oceanographic campaigns linked to a Regional Facility."@en .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#SeriesOfOceanographicCampaigns> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "En serie med havforskningskampanjer knyttet til en regional infrastruktur."@no .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#SeriesOfOceanographicCampaigns> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "O serie de campanii oceanografice asociate unei infrastructuri regionale."@ro .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#SeriesOfOceanographicCampaigns> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Uma série de campanhas oceanográficas associadas a uma infraestrutura regional."@pt .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#SeriesOfOceanographicCampaigns> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Una serie de campañas oceanográficas vinculadas a una instalación regional."@es .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#SeriesOfOceanographicCampaigns> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Una serie di campagne oceanografiche collegate a una struttura regionale."@it .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#SeriesOfOceanographicCampaigns> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Une série de campagnes océanographiques liées à un noeud régional."@fr .
