<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Billion_mooring> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Această platformă nu face parte nici din rețeaua EMSO-France, nici din rețeaua EMSO-ERIC"@ro .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Billion_mooring> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Ce mouillage ne fait ni partie du réseau EMSO-France, ni du réseau EMSO-ERIC"@fr .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Billion_mooring> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Denne plattformen er ikke en del av verken EMSO-France-nettverket eller EMSO-ERIC-nettverket"@no .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Billion_mooring> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Esta plataforma não faz parte nem da rede EMSO-France nem da rede EMSO-ERIC"@pt .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Billion_mooring> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Este amarre no forma parte ni de la red EMSO-France ni de la red EMSO-ERIC"@es .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Billion_mooring> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Questa piattaforma non fa parte né della rete EMSO-France né della rete EMSO-ERIC"@it .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Billion_mooring> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "This mooring is not part of either the EMSO-France network or the EMSO-ERIC network"@en .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Billion_mooring> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Η πλατφόρμα αυτή δεν ανήκει ούτε στο δίκτυο EMSO-France ούτε στο δίκτυο EMSO-ERIC"@el .
