# https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Lion_mooring
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Lion_mooring> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Lion_mooring> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Platform> .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Lion_mooring> <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#hasPlatformCategory> <http://vocab.nerc.ac.uk/collection/L06/current/48/> .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Lion_mooring> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Această platformă aparține exclusiv rețelei EMSO-France și nu face parte din rețeaua EMSO-ERIC"@ro .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Lion_mooring> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Ce mouillage appartient exclusivement au réseau EMSO-France et ne fait pas partie du réseau EMSO-ERIC"@fr .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Lion_mooring> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Denne plattformen tilhører utelukkende EMSO-France-nettverket og er ikke en del av EMSO-ERIC-nettverket"@no .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Lion_mooring> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Esta plataforma pertence exclusivamente à rede EMSO-France e não faz parte da rede EMSO-ERIC"@pt .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Lion_mooring> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Este amarre pertenece exclusivamente a la red EMSO-France y no forma parte de la red EMSO-ERIC"@es .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Lion_mooring> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Questa piattaforma appartiene esclusivamente alla rete EMSO-France e non fa parte della rete EMSO-ERIC"@it .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Lion_mooring> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "This mooring belongs exclusively to the EMSO-France network and is not part of the EMSO-ERIC network"@en .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Lion_mooring> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Η πλατφόρμα αυτή ανήκει αποκλειστικά στο δίκτυο EMSO-France και δεν αποτελεί μέρος του δικτύου EMSO-ERIC"@el .
