<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#OBSEA> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "OBSEA is a cabled seafloor observatory located 4 km off the Vilanova i la Geltru coast in a fishing protected area. It is connected to the coast by an energy and communications mixed cable (OceanOPS WMO number: 6103565)."@en .
