<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#REVOSIMA> <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Project_is_led_by_an_Organization> <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#BRGM> .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#REVOSIMA> <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Project_is_led_by_an_Organization> <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#CNRS> .
