<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#REVOSIMA> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "REVOSIMA er overvåkingsnettverket for vulkanologi og seismologi på Mayotte, som støtter kontinuerlig observasjon av pågående seismo-vulkansk aktivitet."@no .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#REVOSIMA> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "REVOSIMA es la red de vigilancia volcanológica y sismológica de Mayotte que apoya la observación continua de la actividad sismo-volcánica en curso."@es .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#REVOSIMA> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "REVOSIMA est le réseau de surveillance volcanologique et sismologique de Mayotte assurant le suivi continu de l’activité sismo-volcanique en cours."@fr .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#REVOSIMA> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "REVOSIMA este rețeaua de monitorizare vulcanologică și seismologică din Mayotte, care susține observarea continuă a activității seismo-vulcanice în desfășurare."@ro .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#REVOSIMA> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "REVOSIMA is the Mayotte volcanological and seismological monitoring network supporting continuous observation of the ongoing seismo-volcanic activity."@en .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#REVOSIMA> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "REVOSIMA è la rete di monitoraggio vulcanologico e sismologico di Mayotte che supporta l’osservazione continua dell’attività sismo-vulcanica in corso."@it .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#REVOSIMA> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "REVOSIMA é a rede de monitorização vulcanológica e sismológica de Mayotte, que apoia a observação contínua da atividade sismo-vulcânica em curso."@pt .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#REVOSIMA> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Το REVOSIMA είναι το δίκτυο ηφαιστειολογικής και σεισμολογικής παρακολούθησης της Μαγιότ, που υποστηρίζει τη συνεχή παρατήρηση της εν εξελίξει σεισμοηφαιστειακής δραστηριότητας."@el .
